query:
UPDATE standalone_exercises SET 
  moduleId = CASE 
    WHEN uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-SUB-%' THEN 90002
    WHEN uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-DIV-%' THEN 3
    WHEN uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-POR-%' THEN 120006
    WHEN uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-FRA-%' THEN 120001
    WHEN uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-PRO-%' THEN 120003
    WHEN uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-POT-%' OR uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-RAD-%' THEN 120004
    WHEN uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-INT-%' THEN 120005
    WHEN uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-MUL-%' OR uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-EXP-%' THEN 120005
    ELSE moduleId
  END
WHERE uniqueId LIKE 'EX-ARIT-%';
